title: Summer League Vibes | Real Ones
description:
Logan and Raja tell all kinds of stories from summer leagues past and present, then get into the drama between LeBron and Russell Westbrook from Vegas and Raja gives us the real down low on why he defends Russ so hard.
Hosts: Logan Murdock and Raja Bell
Producer: Sasha Ashall
